HEADWORD: Width
<hw>Width</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Wide</er>.]</ety> <def>The quality of being wide; extent from side
to side; breadth; wideness; <as>as, the <ex>width</ex> of cloth; the
<ex>width</ex> of a door</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

